-------------

Please report bugs into MATE bugzilla:
http://bugzilla.mate.org/

Translations
------------

If you have translated Gnote, please contact the corresponding team:

http://l10n.mate.org/teams/

Mailing list
------------

There is a mailing list for gnote. More info here:
http://mail.mate.org/mailman/listinfo/gnote-list

